## イベントサウンド [#e8ec9e71]

### DefineSound [#DefineSound]
|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Header|RECORDHEADER|タグタイプ = 14|
|SoundId|UI16|ID for this sound.|
|SoundFormat|UB[4]|Format of SoundData. See&br;“Audio coding formats”&br;on page 201.|
|SoundRate|UB[2]|The sampling rate. This is&br;ignored for Nellymoser and&br;Speex codecs.&br;5.5kHz is not allowed for MP3.&br;0 = 5.5 kHz&br;1 = 11 kHz&br;2 = 22 kHz&br;3 = 44 kHz|
|SoundSize|UB[1]|Size of each sample. This&br;parameter only pertains to&br;uncompressed formats. This is&br;ignored for compressed&br;formats which always decode&br;to 16 bits internally.&br;0 = snd8Bit&br;1 = snd16Bit|
|SoundType|UB[1]|Mono or stereo sound&br;This is ignored for Nellymoser&br;and Speex.&br;0 = sndMono&br;1 = sndStereo|
|SoundSampleCount|UI32|Number of samples. Not&br;affected by mono/stereo&br;setting; for stereo sounds this is&br;the number of sample pairs.|
|SoundData|UI8[size of sound data]|The sound data; varies by&br;format.|

### StartSound [#StartSound]
|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Header|RECORDHEADER|タグタイプ = 15.|
|SoundId|UI16|ID of sound character to play.|
|SoundInfo|SOUNDINFO|Sound style information.|

### StartSound2 [#StartSound2]
|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Header|RECORDHEADER|タグタイプ = 89.|
|SoundClassName|STRING|Name of the sound class to&br;play.|
|SoundInfo|SOUNDINFO|Sound style information.|

### SOUNDINFO [#SOUNDINFO]
|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Reserved|UB[2]|Always 0.|
|SyncStop|UB[1]|Stop the sound now.|
|SyncNoMultiple|UB[1]|Don’t start the sound if already&br;playing.|
|HasEnvelope|UB[1]|Has envelope information.|
|HasLoops|UB[1]|Has loop information.|
|HasOutPoint|UB[1]|Has out-point information.|
|HasInPoint|UB[1]|Has in-point information.|
|InPoint|If HasInPoint, UI32|Number of samples to skip at&br;beginning of sound.|
|OutPoint|If HasOutPoint, UI32|Position in samples of last&br;sample to play.|
|LoopCount|If HasLoops, UI16|Sound loop count.|
|EnvPoints|If HasEnvelope, UI8|Sound Envelope point count.|
|EnvelopeRecords|If HasEnvelope,&br;SOUNDENVELOPE[EnvPoints]|Sound Envelope records.|

### SOUNDENVELOPE [#SOUNDENVELOPE]
|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Pos44|UI32|Position of envelope point&br;as a number of 44 kHz&br;samples. Multiply&br;accordingly if using a&br;sampling rate less than 44&br;kHz.|
|LeftLevel|UI16|Volume level for left&br;channel. Minimum is 0,&br;maximum is 32768.|
|RightLevel|UI16|Volume level for right&br;channel. Minimum is 0,&br;maximum is 32768.|
